      "picks_file": "picks/picks-2026-06-14-1742.md",
      "why_text": "ESPN analyst Monica McNutt drew online heat for comments touching on Taylor Swift's cultural footprint around the NBA Finals, and freshly-minted Finals MVP Jalen Brunson used his platform moment to publicly back her \u2014 telling critics to cut her some slack. It's a notable move because athletes almost never wade into media-critic pile-ons, especially during the glow of a championship run. Brunson choosing this fight signals both his comfort with his own cultural standing and a broader tension in sports media between traditional analysis and the Taylor Swift-ification of the NBA's fanbase.",
